In order to add support for the Amlogic GXL/GXM USB Glue, this adds
the corresponding :
- PHY names
- clock names
- USB2 PHY init and mode set
- regmap setup

Signed-off-by: Neil Armstrong <narmstrong@baylibre.com>
---
